{"tw": {"3606750": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Succubus Crisis", "steam_appid": 3606750, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/6d337e644e4331abb70a8208b384a03d.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魅魔雷姆莉亞與族人不同，她心地善良，不願傷害獵物，也無法對不義之事視若無睹。某日，她救出了被奴役的半精靈亞莉安黛兒。但她很快發現，自己的村莊也正陷入危機。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兩人踏上旅途，為了拯救魅魔村莊與被奴役的精靈，並揭露敵人的真正目的。然而，亞莉安黛兒正遭受強大精神詛咒「靈魂破碎者」折磨，唯有雷姆莉亞能暫時緩解。要徹底解開詛咒，她們必須追查施術者的真身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/9f1b833cbe37d5cf03093da7a850ce8c.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作擁有兩種模式：劇情模式與RPG模式。在劇情模式中，享受故事，了解角色。在RPG模式中探索世界、擊敗敵人，推進劇情發展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >先發制人能在回合制戰鬥中取得優勢。善用策略與資源，方能克服難關，持續前進。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/e99a569ea38c6b3dcd4eeba05910c22e.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/4697d25ed7601580fd4788107ad33b77.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/b066d5030bd7112f82374471cba858e4.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/0befc5035a217a3aeb8b8b2346f97700.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/8078c12006851d4af8f78054f462d29c.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>動畫H場景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >盡情欣賞高品質動態演出，讓你的觀賞體驗更加火熱與深刻！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>回憶房間</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >劇情不會錯過任何一幕！已解鎖的場景都能在回憶房中重複欣賞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>視覺小說模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切換至經典視覺小說介面，支援對話紀錄、存檔、隱藏視窗等便利功能，輕鬆享受劇情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>仁慈的續戰設計</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使戰敗，也能以1HP繼續前進。若資源耗盡，也可選擇從地圖開頭重啟並恢復資源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>隨時存檔</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不論何時都可手動存檔，安心遊玩，進度不怕丟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/6d337e644e4331abb70a8208b384a03d.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魅魔雷姆莉亞與族人不同，她心地善良，不願傷害獵物，也無法對不義之事視若無睹。某日，她救出了被奴役的半精靈亞莉安黛兒。但她很快發現，自己的村莊也正陷入危機。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兩人踏上旅途，為了拯救魅魔村莊與被奴役的精靈，並揭露敵人的真正目的。然而，亞莉安黛兒正遭受強大精神詛咒「靈魂破碎者」折磨，唯有雷姆莉亞能暫時緩解。要徹底解開詛咒，她們必須追查施術者的真身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/9f1b833cbe37d5cf03093da7a850ce8c.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作擁有兩種模式：劇情模式與RPG模式。在劇情模式中，享受故事，了解角色。在RPG模式中探索世界、擊敗敵人，推進劇情發展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >先發制人能在回合制戰鬥中取得優勢。善用策略與資源，方能克服難關，持續前進。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/e99a569ea38c6b3dcd4eeba05910c22e.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/4697d25ed7601580fd4788107ad33b77.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/b066d5030bd7112f82374471cba858e4.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/0befc5035a217a3aeb8b8b2346f97700.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/8078c12006851d4af8f78054f462d29c.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>動畫H場景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >盡情欣賞高品質動態演出，讓你的觀賞體驗更加火熱與深刻！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>回憶房間</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >劇情不會錯過任何一幕！已解鎖的場景都能在回憶房中重複欣賞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>視覺小說模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切換至經典視覺小說介面，支援對話紀錄、存檔、隱藏視窗等便利功能，輕鬆享受劇情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>仁慈的續戰設計</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使戰敗，也能以1HP繼續前進。若資源耗盡，也可選擇從地圖開頭重啟並恢復資源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>隨時存檔</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不論何時都可手動存檔，安心遊玩，進度不怕丟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "扮演善良的魅魔雷姆莉亞，與半精靈亞莉安黛兒結伴，拯救魅魔村莊並解放被奴役的精靈。黑暗奇幻RPG，講述友情與成長的旅程。", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/18c1648a42b8b7bfca2896db1d6de348ee614d93/header.jpg?t=1771575393", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/c3ba1b6757fbf7644f2405007d8e7cddfee4b68e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1771575393", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/c3ba1b6757fbf7644f2405007d8e7cddfee4b68e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1771575393", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["Fantasy Land"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 18800, "final": 18800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 188"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2026 年 2 月 13 日"}}}}, "us": {"3606750": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Succubus Crisis", "steam_appid": 3606750, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/9ec6e02b034cd8ab0f529598a50eaa74.poster.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/9ec6e02b034cd8ab0f529598a50eaa74.webm?t=1771575393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/4eff358b9cde4bfa48f4904543f8c01e.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A kind-hearted succubus, Remuria, an outlier among the succubi, won't kill her prey and cannot ignore injustice. One day, she helps Ariandelle, a half-elf slave, escape captivity. However, Remuria soon discovers that her own village is also in danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teaming up with Ariandelle, the two set out on a journey with shared goals: to free all the enslaved elves, defend the succubi village, and uncover their enemy's ultimate goal. But that's not the end of their struggle, as Ariandelle is afflicted with Soul Crusher—a powerful mental spell that only Remuria can temporarily alleviate with her special powers. To break the spell completely, they must track down the caster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/6221b5756ad06bb65570168ee11ab6e7.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the game in two separate modes. Enjoy the story in Novel Mode, where you follow the plot and get to know the characters. In RPG Mode you can explore, fight enemies, and work to push the story forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack enemies first to gain the upper hand with a preemptive strike, giving you an advantage in turn-based battles. Plan ahead to use your resources carefully to overcome tough challenges and keep moving forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/363e5c4692328bd3e5cf16b0a92b748e.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/1602e33aca16b0157265de0258715258.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/8e52b9953ed790fc3db9b656dc02c909.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/bbf7b374ce91686383c2789045b48aa4.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/a92e7af2c29e915014aa2ba83973f7d5.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Animated H-Scenes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a hot collection of beautifully animated scenes to enhance your viewing pleasure!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Recollection Room</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nothing is lost in the story! Every unlocked scene can be revisited and watched again through the Recollection Room.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Novel Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this mode, you can enjoy all scenes with a traditional Visual Novel interface and its features, including LOG, SAVE, and HIDE Window.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Merciful Second Chances</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if you lose a battle, you can continue playing with 1 HP. If you're out of resources, the game allows you to restart from the beginning of the map with your resources rolled back.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Save Anywhere</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game allows you to save anytime you want, so don’t worry about losing your progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/9ec6e02b034cd8ab0f529598a50eaa74.poster.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/9ec6e02b034cd8ab0f529598a50eaa74.webm?t=1771575393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/4eff358b9cde4bfa48f4904543f8c01e.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A kind-hearted succubus, Remuria, an outlier among the succubi, won't kill her prey and cannot ignore injustice. One day, she helps Ariandelle, a half-elf slave, escape captivity. However, Remuria soon discovers that her own village is also in danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teaming up with Ariandelle, the two set out on a journey with shared goals: to free all the enslaved elves, defend the succubi village, and uncover their enemy's ultimate goal. But that's not the end of their struggle, as Ariandelle is afflicted with Soul Crusher—a powerful mental spell that only Remuria can temporarily alleviate with her special powers. To break the spell completely, they must track down the caster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/6221b5756ad06bb65570168ee11ab6e7.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the game in two separate modes. Enjoy the story in Novel Mode, where you follow the plot and get to know the characters. In RPG Mode you can explore, fight enemies, and work to push the story forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack enemies first to gain the upper hand with a preemptive strike, giving you an advantage in turn-based battles. Plan ahead to use your resources carefully to overcome tough challenges and keep moving forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/363e5c4692328bd3e5cf16b0a92b748e.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/1602e33aca16b0157265de0258715258.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/8e52b9953ed790fc3db9b656dc02c909.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/bbf7b374ce91686383c2789045b48aa4.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/extras/a92e7af2c29e915014aa2ba83973f7d5.avif?t=1771575393\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Animated H-Scenes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a hot collection of beautifully animated scenes to enhance your viewing pleasure!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Recollection Room</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nothing is lost in the story! Every unlocked scene can be revisited and watched again through the Recollection Room.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Novel Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this mode, you can enjoy all scenes with a traditional Visual Novel interface and its features, including LOG, SAVE, and HIDE Window.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Merciful Second Chances</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if you lose a battle, you can continue playing with 1 HP. If you're out of resources, the game allows you to restart from the beginning of the map with your resources rolled back.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Save Anywhere</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game allows you to save anytime you want, so don’t worry about losing your progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "In this turn-based RPG, play as Remuria, a kind-hearted succubus, who teams up with the half-elf Ariandelle in their shared goal to save the succubi village and free enslaved elves. It's a tale of tender friendship, personal growth, and passion set in a captivating, dark fantasy world.", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/18c1648a42b8b7bfca2896db1d6de348ee614d93/header.jpg?t=1771575393", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/c3ba1b6757fbf7644f2405007d8e7cddfee4b68e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1771575393", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3606750/c3ba1b6757fbf7644f2405007d8e7cddfee4b68e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1771575393", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["Fantasy Land"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "USD", "initial": 999, "final": 999, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "$9.99"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "Single-player"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam Achievements"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam Cloud"}, {"id": 62, "description": "Family Sharing"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "Adventure"}, {"id": "3", "description": "RPG"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "Feb 13, 2026"}}}}, "fetched_at": "2026-04-23T06:25:53Z"}